name: $resourceType
desc: Returns the FHIR type name for this instance

name: $identifier
desc: Returns: Business identifier for the marketing authorization, as assigned by a regulator.

name: $addidentifier
desc: Business identifier for the marketing authorization, as assigned by a regulator.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: Business identifier for the marketing authorization, as assigned by a regulator.

name: $subject
desc: Returns: The product that is being authorized.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The product that is being authorized.

name: $::type
desc: Returns: Type of this authorization, for example drug marketing approval, orphan drug designation.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: Type of this authorization, for example drug marketing approval, orphan drug designation.

name: $description
desc: Returns: General textual supporting information.

name: $region
desc: Returns: The region (country, jurisdiction etc.) in which the marketing authorization has been granted.

name: $addregion
desc: The region (country, jurisdiction etc.) in which the marketing authorization has been granted.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: The region (country, jurisdiction etc.) in which the marketing authorization has been granted.

name: $status
desc: Returns: The status of the marketing authorization.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The status of the marketing authorization.

name: $statusDate
desc: Returns: The date at which the given status has become applicable.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The date at which the given status has become applicable.

name: $validityPeriod
desc: Returns: The beginning of the time period in which the marketing authorization is in the specific status shall be specified A complete date consisting of day, month and year shall be specified using the ISO 8601 date format.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The beginning of the time period in which the marketing authorization is in the specific status shall be specified A complete date consisting of day, month and year shall be specified using the ISO 8601 date format.

name: $basis
desc: Returns: The legal framework against which this authorization is granted, or other reasons for it.

name: $addbasis
desc: The legal framework against which this authorization is granted, or other reasons for it.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: The legal framework against which this authorization is granted, or other reasons for it.

name: $relatedDate
desc: Returns: Other dates associated with the authorization. It is common for an authorization to have renewal dates, initial time limited phases and so on.

name: $addrelatedDate
desc: Other dates associated with the authorization. It is common for an authorization to have renewal dates, initial time limited phases and so on.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: Other dates associated with the authorization. It is common for an authorization to have renewal dates, initial time limited phases and so on.

name: $jurisdictionalAuthorization
desc: Returns: Authorization in areas within a country.

name: $addjurisdictionalAuthorization
desc: Authorization in areas within a country.

lvardefs.name: objRef
lvardefs.desc: Authorization in areas within a country.

name: $holder
desc: Returns: Marketing Authorization Holder.

name: $regulator
desc: Returns: Medicines Regulatory Agency.

name: $case
desc: Returns: The case or regulatory procedure for granting or amending a marketing authorization.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The case or regulatory procedure for granting or amending a marketing authorization.
